	<h1 class="title">今日应用：想要离开新闻，可以试试简单清新的“单读”</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/1375/small/1375.jpg?1460641790" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">徐弢</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-09-18 08:37:15 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/2416/medium/2416.jpg?1436650952" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="2416" data-title="《今日应用：想要离开新闻，可以试试简单清新的“单读”》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/2416/medium/2416.jpg?1436650952" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/2416.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
